::Hot Rod:: 

Finally reached the Cybertronian Fire.
"Man, its good to be back."
He opened his comm.
"Prowl, its Hot Rod. I'm back. Is there anything going on that you could
use a hand with?"

::Demolition::

He dug himself out of the sea floor.
"I'm going to kill that Maximal!"
He started swimming back to the island.
